 <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዕለተ፡ ረክብ</foreign> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">ʿǝlata rakb</t:quote></cit> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">holiday that is celebrated at mid-Pentecost or on a Wednesday that comes 24 days after Ester</t:quote></cit>, <lbl expand="videas">vid.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ረክብ፡</foreign> <bibl><ptr target="bm:Leslau1987dic"/><citedRange unit="page"> 469a</citedRange></bibl> 
